{"tid":1602920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支國國慶閱兵要賀一賀佢","createTime":"2019-09-29T14:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T14:37:29.000Z","uid":6352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a9c3bdef0578a51c72c60d216298eb272f10c5fe","tid":1602920,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:27:35.000Z","msg":"支國國慶閱兵時間未公佈，但上兩次（2009,2015)都係早上10點開始。到時全球的新聞都會留意，如果香港同時間有遊行，相信一定對落支國面子有幫助。<br />\n但我見10月1日大部分活動都集中係1點後，大家有咩建議，可以叫一部分人提早慶祝？"},{"pid":"9db1df0b2a74a2f4fc4d5dc98510799d241b9397","tid":1602920,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:28:57.000Z","msg":"唔好睇輕國慶閱兵，1984年後停左，2000年打後只搞過2次，支國重視過奧運開幕禮。"},{"pid":"33578abbf02d0712d0723b68b7214ce591be6f9f","tid":1602920,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:30:10.000Z","msg":"中國唔似俄羅斯年年搞，習大大好重視架，千其唔好分薄收視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4140b9ef53c5b46d1017c808b9b8a219f8a5264e","tid":1602920,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:32:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0ffca9629adb6a92ea36022e615dc1a13cc3797","tid":1602920,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33578abbf02d0712d0723b68b7214ce591be6f9f","tid":1602920,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:30:10.000Z","msg":"中國唔似俄羅斯年年搞，習大大好重視架，千其唔好分薄收視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:37:29.000Z","msg":"2000年打後北京得兩次大型閱兵<br />\n2009年 建國60年 同 2015 抗戰勝利70年<br />\n仲要事前宣傳左咁耐<br />\n肯定要賀一賀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}